Localization.Name: Deri Gloves Arctic
Localization.Description: Maintain a tactile sense of the world while also keeping your hands safe and dry with the Deri fingerless gloves. Featuring a comfortable inner lining, lightweight plating on the back of the hand and slip resistant palm padding, the Deri gloves are an ideal choice for a wide variety of tasks.
